{"id":220,"ayahs":[{"number":98,"arabic":"فَلَوْلَا كَانَتْ قَرْيَةٌ ءَامَنَتْ فَنَفَعَهَآ إِيمَٰنُهَآ إِلَّا قَوْمَ يُونُسَ لَمَّآ ءَامَنُوا۟ كَشَفْنَا عَنْهُمْ عَذَابَ ٱلْخِزْىِ فِى ٱلْحَيَوٰةِ ٱلدُّنْيَا وَمَتَّعْنَٰهُمْ إِلَىٰ حِينٍۢ","translation":"For, alas, there has never yet been any community that attained to faith [in its entirety,] and thereupon benefited by its faith, except the people of Jonah. When they came to believe, We removed from them the suffering of disgrace [which otherwise would have befallen them even] in the life of this world, and allowed them to enjoy their life during the time allotted to them.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1462.mp3","surahId":10,"words":[{"id":70792,"position":1,"arabic":"فَلَوْلَا","translation":"অতঃপর কেন না","audioUrl":"wbw/010_098_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70793,"position":2,"arabic":"كَانَتْ","translation":"(এমন) হলো যে","audioUrl":"wbw/010_098_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70794,"position":3,"arabic":"قَرْيَةٌ","translation":"জনপদবাসী","audioUrl":"wbw/010_098_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70795,"position":4,"arabic":"ءَامَنَتْ","translation":"(শাস্তি আসার পূর্বেই) ঈমান আনতো","audioUrl":"wbw/010_098_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70796,"position":5,"arabic":"فَنَفَعَهَآ","translation":"তাহ'লে উপকারে আসতো তার","audioUrl":"wbw/010_098_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70797,"position":6,"arabic":"إِيمَـٰنُهَآ","translation":"তার ঈমান (আনা)","audioUrl":"wbw/010_098_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70798,"position":7,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"তবে (ব্যতিক্রম)","audioUrl":"wbw/010_098_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70799,"position":8,"arabic":"قَوْمَ","translation":"জাতি","audioUrl":"wbw/010_098_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70800,"position":9,"arabic":"يُونُسَ","translation":"ইউনুসের","audioUrl":"wbw/010_098_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":70801,"position":10,"arabic":"لَمَّآ","translation":"যখন (শাস্তি দেখে